#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.ellip\\_harm"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:1 of
msgid "Ellipsoidal harmonic functions E^p_n(l)"
msgstr "椭球调和函数 E^p_n(l)"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:3 of
msgid ""
"These are also known as Lame functions of the first kind, and are "
"solutions to the Lame equation:"
msgstr "这些函数也被称为第一类拉梅函数，是拉梅方程的解："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:6 of
msgid ""
"(s^2 - h^2)(s^2 - k^2)E''(s)\n"
"+ s(2s^2 - h^2 - k^2)E'(s) + (a - q s^2)E(s) = 0\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:9 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`q = (n+1)n` and :math:`a` is the eigenvalue (not returned) "
"corresponding to the solutions."
msgstr "其中 :math:`q = (n+1)n`，:math:`a` 是对应解的特征值（不返回）。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:12 of
msgid "``h**2``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:14 of
msgid "``k**2``; should be larger than ``h**2``"
msgstr "``k**2``；应大于 ``h**2``"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:16 of
msgid "Degree"
msgstr "度数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:18 of
msgid "Coordinate"
msgstr "坐标"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:20 of
msgid "Order, can range between [1,2n+1]"
msgstr "阶数，范围在 [1,2n+1] 之间"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:22
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:24 of
msgid "Sign of prefactor of functions. Can be +/-1. See Notes."
msgstr "函数前因子的符号，可以是 +/-1。详见说明。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:27 of
msgid "**E** -- the harmonic :math:`E^p_n(s)`"
msgstr "**E** -- 调和函数 :math:`E^p_n(s)`"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellip_harm_2`, :py:obj:`ellip_normal`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:34 of
msgid ""
"The geometric interpretation of the ellipsoidal functions is explained in"
" [2]_, [3]_, [4]_. The `signm` and `signn` arguments control the sign of "
"prefactors for functions according to their type::"
msgstr ""
"椭球函数的几何解释见 [2]_, [3]_, [4]_。`signm` 和 `signn` 参数根据函数"
"类型控制前因子的符号::"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:44 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:45 of
msgid ""
"Digital Library of Mathematical Functions 29.12 "
"https://dlmf.nist.gov/29.12"
msgstr "数学函数数字图书馆 29.12 https://dlmf.nist.gov/29.12"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:47 of
msgid ""
"Bardhan and Knepley, \"Computational science and re-discovery: open-"
"source implementations of ellipsoidal harmonics for problems in potential"
" theory\", Comput. Sci. Disc. 5, 014006 (2012) "
":doi:`10.1088/1749-4699/5/1/014006`."
msgstr ""
"Bardhan 和 Knepley，“计算科学与重新发现：用于势论问题的椭球调和函数开源"
"实现”，Comput. Sci. Disc. 5, 014006 (2012) :doi:`10.1088/1749-4699/5/1/"
"014006`."

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:52 of
msgid ""
"David J.and Dechambre P, \"Computation of Ellipsoidal Gravity Field "
"Harmonics for small solar system bodies\" pp. 30-36, 2000"
msgstr ""
"David J. 和 Dechambre P，“小太阳系天体重力场椭球调和函数的计算”，第 30-"
"36 页，2000 年"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_harm.ellip_harm:55 of
msgid ""
"George Dassios, \"Ellipsoidal Harmonics: Theory and Applications\" pp. "
"418, 2012"
msgstr "George Dassios，《椭球调和函数：理论与应用》，第 418 页，2012 年"

